<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>成功案例 - 恒昇留学商务</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #f7f8fa;
            color: #333;
        }
        /* 头部 */
        .header {
            background: #1a2b48;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        /* 导航 */
        .nav {
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .nav a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .nav a:hover {
            color: #1a2b48;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        /* 标题区 */
        .case-title {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0 20px;
        }
        .case-title h2 {
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #1a2b48;
        }
        .case-title p {
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        /* 案例卡片容器 */
        .case-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        /* 卡片样式 */
        .case-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .case-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
        }
        .case-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .case-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .case-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #eef2fb;
            color: #1a2b48;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .case-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .case-desc {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .case-result {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #27ae60;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        /* 底部 */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #1a2b48;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>恒昇留学商务（香港）有限公司</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="nav">
        <a href="#">首页</a>
        <a href="#">关于我们</a>
        <a href="#">服务项目</a>
        <a href="#" style="color:#1a2b48;font-weight:bold;">成功案例</a>
